name: Ceci n’est pas une Rorschach test, it’s a digitized inkstain on paper
description: In 2017 I asked a computer (deepdream) how it perceived a Rorschach test. Instead of saying a digitized inkstain on paper it gave me a weird hallucination. Any 20th century psychologist would classify this computer as a psychopath... yet we trust these algorithms with our deepest and dearest thoughts.
